data.description:
Charming 3 bedroom home with cottage vibe and nautical accents.  Beautiful refinished hardwood floors, large kitchen with breakfast nook, coved ceiling in living room.  All kitchen appliances stay.  Updates include most windows, breaker panel.  Updates soon to be completed: 
 new roof and siding to be completed soon. This home has been very well maintained and is in move in condition, with immediate occupancy.  Located right by Friendship Park and Lake Erie, this home offers the best of Point Place living all around you!
